### List all guests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests

### Create guest (noivo side)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João",
  "sobrenome": "Silva",
  "telefone": "11999999999",
  "relacionamento": "noivo"
}

### Create guest (noiva side)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/guests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria",
  "sobrenome": "Santos",
  "telefone": "11888888888",
  "relacionamento": "noiva"
}

### Get guest by ID (replace with a real ID from the list response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests/REPLACE-WITH-UUID

### Update guest — confirm attendance
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/guests/REPLACE-WITH-UUID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirmacao": true
}

### Update guest — change phone
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/guests/REPLACE-WITH-UUID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefone": "11777777777"
}

### Delete guest
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/guests/REPLACE-WITH-UUID

### Import CSV
POST http://localhost:8080/api/guests/import
